A standalone library for producing documents of any text-driven format (html, md, csv, etc.) using a powerful and extensible templating engine.

Quick Start:
1. use PlaceholderTemplateResolver.Create<YOUR_TYPE>(TEMPLATE) to create your template resolver. Templates use {{PROPERTY_PATH}} for placeholders (can be customised).
2. use the Fluent API methods to specify settings/metadata for your templates (optional).
3. call IPlaceholderTemplateResolver<>.Resolve(YOUR_OBJECT) to generate your document.
